:","m":"very much"},{"d":"एतेन:","m":"because of that"},{"d":"जीवितुम्:","m":"survival"},{"d":"शक्यम्:","m":"will be possible"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"केदारस्येवकेदारस्सोदकस्यनिरूदकः ।उपस्नेहेनजीवामिजीवन्तींयच्छृणोमिताम्","trans":"I am living only because of hearing about her survival, just as a paddy field without water gets wet by the proximity of a neighboring paddy field with water.","words":[{"d":"ताम्:","m":"she"},{"d":"जीवन्तीम्:","m":"is living यत्: that"},{"d":"शृणोमि:","m":"I hearing"},{"d":"सोदकस्य:","m":"with water"},{"d":"केदारस्य:","m":"like a paddy field"},{"d":"उपस्नेहेन:","m":"getting wet"},{"d":"निरूदकः","m":"without water"},{"d":"केदारःइवजीवामि:","m":"am living like crop with water"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"कदानुखलुसुश्रोणींशतपत्त्रायतेक्षणाम् ।विजित्यशत्रून्द्रक्ष्यामिसीतास्फीतामिवश्रियम्","trans":"When will I be able to win the enemies and see that Sita of charming limbs, with large and beautiful eyes like lotus petals, who is like an abundance of fortune?","words":[{"d":"शत्रून्:","m":"enemies"},{"d":"विजित्य:","m":"winning"},{"d":"सुश्रोणीम्:","m":"lady with charming limbs"},{"d":"शतपत्रायतेक्षणाम्:","m":"of large beautiful eyes like lotus petals"},{"d":"स्फीताम्:","m":"abundance of"},{"d":"श्रियमिव:","m":"like fortune"},{"d":"सीताम्:","m":"Sita"},{"d":"कदानुखलु:","m":"when indeed"},{"d":"द्रक्ष्यामि:","m":"will be able to see"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"कदानुचारुबिम्बोष्ठंतस्याःपद्ममिवाननम् ।ईषदुन्नम्यपास्यामिरसायनमिवातुरः","trans":"I do not know when I will lift her lotuslike face slightly and drink her beautiful lips like an afflicted man drinks sweet juice.","words":[{"d":"चारुबिम्बोष्ठम्:","m":"beautiful lips like Bimba fruit"},{"d":"पद्ममिव:","m":"lotus like"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"her"},{"d":"आननम्:","m":"face"},{"d":"ईषत्:","m":"slightly"},{"d":"उन्नाम्य:","m":"lifting"},{"d":"आतुरः","m":"one who is afflicted"},{"d":"रसायनमिव:","m":"like a sweet drink"},{"d":"कदा:","m":"when"},{"d":"पास्यामि:","m":"shall I drink?"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तस्यात्तुसंहितौपीनौस्तनौतालफ